text.section:
The following are exempted from the provisions of subsection (d) of this section so long as live entertainment is not offered or provided on more than 8 days in any calendar month:
The room of a registered guest in a hotel or motel;
Property owned by a volunteer fire company;
Property owned and operated by a community or homeowners association comprised solely of property owners in a single subdivision; or
Property owned by a bona fide religious institution.
